{"tid":1666794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用呢個flow解釋彥霖案嘅疑點","createTime":"2019-10-21T06:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T06:39:52.000Z","uid":53808,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3d25edc16f425f33633b1dc44acb678ccd82135f","tid":1666794,"uid":53808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:36:49.000Z","msg":"外藉女手足畀黑警濫暴奪命<br />\n高層為免上升國際層面，決定隱瞞真相，搵替死鬼<br />\n彥霖某啲條件符合，不幸被選中<br />\n港共要脅彥霖至親，唔乖乖哋配合，就唔留彥霖活命<br />\n<br />\n如配合劇本嘅程度由 冇 至 高 粗略分為0、1、2<br />\n就會係：<br />\n<br />\n屍 - 0<br />\n彥霖 - 0<br />\n媽 - 1<br />\n舅 - 1<br />\n黨鐵 - 1<br />\n學校 - 1<br />\ntvb - 1<br />\n蘋果 - 0<br />\n子明 - 0<br />\n報夢巴 - 0<br />\n<br />\n黑警、政府直頭係導演+編劇唔撚使講<br />\n媽、舅、黨鐵、學校、tvb受指示要配合 但知唔晒/該單位唔係全部人知 <br />\n以致執行劇本上論論盡盡、錯漏百出<br />\n<br />\n至於男朋友、男朋友老豆、後父、last seen/heard 朋友，我大膽推測同媽、舅一樣 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟呢個flow諗 啲細位似乎解得通<br />\n利申 純大膽推測，如有明顯bug或已討論過，由佢沉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本人 除專制暴政 別無他敵  <br />\n無論如何 絕不自殺 <br />\n如有不測 必有嫁禍 <br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"983e8223fbebc663bf99920dae012ac4bd6cc470","tid":1666794,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:36:56.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d12ddb86ae1bc1026d63cb3acd92647c79f233","tid":1666794,"uid":53808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:38:53.000Z","msg":"最後，聽晚元朗見"},{"pid":"fb9c945ad73a755e50efd6c45cc334f16b9a89f9","tid":1666794,"uid":53808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"983e8223fbebc663bf99920dae012ac4bd6cc470","tid":1666794,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:36:56.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link